BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:FEET IN THE MUD- WORKSHOP 2
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260420T160000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260420T173000
UID:c902ba0e1973caa1f48e7c0d1d760461@petalumariverpark.org
DESCRIPTION:Reading Historical Newspaper Accounts of Chinese Expulsion\, 1
 850–1890: How Racism Is Naturalized and Taught Learn how racism is natur
 alized\, and explore the effects of such naturalization\, in this hands-on
  activity reading local newspapers on Chinese immigrants across the span o
 f 1850–1890. This lecture will be followed by a group discussion.&nbsp\;
  Limited seating. .fe-block-85475957e674f6699900 {mix-blend-mode: \; } Reg
 ister Here #block-a973df68af2696e0b05e {--sqs-block-content-flex: 0\; } #b
